{
  "text": "Fourth, lack of human awareness (in this study's case, the students), as many studies pointed out, posed another challenge; this included AI's inability to understand the student's context or environment, such as unique writing styles, tone, techniques, communication styles, learning environment, and so on (Endsley, 2000; Jiang et al., 2023).",
